Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新道寺…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫我坐在宮永照的下家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新道寺在攪局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起說「做到了」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不如說是新道寺讓我做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家2300  莊家4200
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千里山的園城寺選手  阻止了冠軍的連莊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了  新道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那張牌是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宣告立直的話  明明可以一發自摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然捨棄了自己的必殺技來和牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  進入南場！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
