Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於後半戰也進入了南場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先鋒戰只剩下四局了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是摸牌就已經這麼費力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,體力一直在下降啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,1300點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有3局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部長  花田那傢伙沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使以自己人角度來看  也還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高中聯賽的正式選手  為什麼是用花田做先鋒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的選手安排感覺與去年也不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經放棄先鋒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾年  我們學校在全國比賽中得不到好成績
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為我們的ACE總是敗給其它學校的ACE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有像是姬松之類遵循傳統將ACE置於中堅位置的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有將ACE放在大將位置上的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說更多的是顛覆傳統而把ACE放在先鋒的位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就一直輸在這點上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去年我就失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才改變了策略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是今年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們按照由弱到強的順序排列出場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄先鋒  老師是這麼安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先鋒為什麼不是我們隊裏排名第五的友清呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得之前與雀士的練習比賽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那兩天中以雀士作為對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻一次也沒有被擊飛的只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（被击飞(箱/トバ)：指失去所有分数棒而被完爆，即0分或以下）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有花田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去問她的時候  她說從沒有失去過所有的點棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙不會被飛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  她被當作棄子放在了先鋒的位置上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花田要是知道的話  肯定會很沮喪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被選為正式選手的時候還很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們只有靠後面四人的火力一決勝負啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被我聽到了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇～好受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…才沒有這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興啊  我擁有著他人所需求的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這不是能讓我成為ACE的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被別人所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再沒有比這更棒的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我被拜託擔當棄子啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的任務是將失點控制在最小限度內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是在不被飛的前提下盡可能強行得分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道！但好有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第五巡是這種牌的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來進攻吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快  好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2600點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有兩局了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到了最終局之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（最终局之前(ラス前)：在半庄战中指南三局）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都做不到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家1300  莊家2600
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才連一巡之後都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經…不行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於進入了最終局！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那位持有著將近二十萬點數的選手…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是那位冠軍的莊家！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到點差會這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我是在說憐的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續這麼下去的話  那傢伙就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,7700點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,園城寺同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千里山的ACE…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐點炮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千里山的園城寺選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有立直的情況下在公開賽中點炮這是首次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正所謂是初體驗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼用這樣的詞來強調？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尾莊繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然根據團體賽的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先鋒戰有這麼大的點差也是正常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說憐…已經看不見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到～達～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  趕快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了  小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快進去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個先進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我一定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廁所的話裏面也有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  小咲  待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來  這已經是冠軍的個人舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次究竟要連莊到什麼時候呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她們幾個差不多應該到會場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…有種強烈的她們坐錯車了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟能不能在先鋒戰結束前趕到呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但完全看不出這場先鋒戰什麼時候能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…冠軍不會就這麼一直連續和牌下去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還不如把哪家擊飛結束得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我們也一直贏下去的話  總有一天將以她為對手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟該怎麼阻止她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白糸台高中的點數已經突破了20萬點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但尾莊莊家的冠軍理所當然的沒有選擇和牌後終止半莊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續連莊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是一個人在蹂躪全場！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,龍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…已經…不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐之值班表？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能幫上ACE的憐  大家一起排的值班表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以此為條件也從醫生那裏拿到合宿的許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然一開始只能在校內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…這樣就可以不用在學校和醫院兩頭跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,合宿時的餐飲已經檢驗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地請教了醫院的營養師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會幫忙做料理的  很擅長的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要力氣的地方就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…雖然很開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得很對不住啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照顧我的事  交給其他人不也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教練雖然也說了交給替補生們去做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得那是最有效率的普遍做法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我們就是想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,船Q…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就這麼在一起的話  說不定會產生什麼神奇效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不科學了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你剛剛不是才說了沒效率的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒效率和不科學是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.47,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有什麼不同啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是隊友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏待著的話  會被蚊子咬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得睡覺好浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天不能洗個清晨澡也很浪費吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熬夜的話就兩邊都不浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過明天就會很難受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就在這裏優雅地感受夜晚的涼風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到燈光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧  能看到河對面星星點點的燈光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏每一盞燈光都是一個家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這就是生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定全是路燈或者信號燈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我誤會一下也好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在去年高中聯賽失利後回程的飛機上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從窗口向外望去  家鄉的燈火一覽無遺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏面是否有一個人在為我加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到這裏就感到無地自容  止不住的悲傷和悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不像話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但這不就是高中聯賽的魅力之處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇  好冷淡的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果真像夕說的那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐飛機回去的時候我也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛好輪到我摸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一巡也沒錯過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是走馬燈一樣的感覺嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總算一向聽了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要被自摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每人4100點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是冠軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與第二位的分差已經達到了13萬點！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也阻止不了這隻怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玄…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小玄…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  玄姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最終局二本場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,獵物不死不鬆手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還將繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直至某人的氣息被終結為止！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她正是如此的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的時候明明就沒看屏幕吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又稍微能看到一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的和牌是12300點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  下次就是18600點以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不拼不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再這樣讓宮永照連莊下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去有人會被飛  比賽也就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我能拿到第二位的概率
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及之後大家奪回失點拿到第二位以上的概率…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腦筋沒有好到能去計算這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我還是明白一件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是選擇我自己能接受的那一種！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓任何人被飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一次都沒和牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去  一點都幫不上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看起來那麼的難過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你可是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為阿知賀攥住了寶牌  其它的牌路才那麼容易猜透
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冠軍無法借助寶牌提高得分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也到了需要強行提高得點的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是這樣的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牌…有那麼重嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活著好辛苦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年紀輕輕就領悟了世間的真理吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我們就是想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就這麼在一起的話  說不定會產生什麼神奇效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但這不就是高中聯賽的魅力之處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是大家贈予我的一巡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓我任性一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Triple　{\r}\N三重效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三巡之後！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:03.97,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Image...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:08.15,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}加速して行く未来に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:14.65,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}描いてく奇跡の形
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:19.85,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君と手を繋いでるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:26.42,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}諦めるなんてありえないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:31.65,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}手のひらには　戦いあって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:37.53,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}積み重なった傷跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:40.71,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}さぁ、いこう？旅をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:49.13,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}銀河が残してきた記憶に新たなる一手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:55.87,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}こぼれ響く音がリズムになって　夢咲かせようと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:01.47,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}フィールドを歌うわ　so futuristic player
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:04.63,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重なる想い　次の笑顔へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.55,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}そう、確かな勝利へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:10.63,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}エールになるように　指を絡めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:17.65,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}辿りついて　Over future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:03.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Image...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:08.15,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}寄宿在加速的未來中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:14.65,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}描繪出奇跡的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:19.85,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}雖然與你兩手相牽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:26.42,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也絕對無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:31.65,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}手心之中　奏響戰鬥的樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:37.53,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}喚醒經久積累的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:40.71,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那麼　出發前行吧？開始一段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:49.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}為銀河之中殘留的記憶刻下嶄新的一式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:55.87,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}飄零的音聲交集成旋律　由我們來尋找夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:01.47,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}唱響起原野之歌　so futuristic player
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:04.63,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重疊的思緒　匯作下次的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.55,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}是的　指引著那必然的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:10.63,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}十指緊扣　彼此聲援
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:17.65,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}終將抵達那　Over future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  進不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是到了半決賽  一大早就這麼熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此  只好用小和的胸部之力來開闢道路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼能力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  依舊那樣播報就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～總是那麼生氣的話胸部會氣鼓起來的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓不起來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:52.74,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}會鼓起來的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
